http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Visakhapatnam/Award-for-VSP/article14636406.ece

The Visakhapatnam Steel Plant has received the CIO-100 award from the International Data Group (IDG), the largest technology media, events and research company in the world which honours 100 companies that demonstrate excellence and achievement in IT.The award was presented in recognition of VSP’s operational and strategic excellence in Information Technology (IT) shown during the year and was received by General Manager (IT) K.V.S.S. Rajeswara Rao during the 11{+t}{+h}annual CIO symposium held in Pune.